
1  

Akirot naka enabi Yeremia naatemari Baruk okoku loka Neria, naewadikaa oitabo akiro nu nuka aituk naka Yeretnia, kokaru lokiwoŋonet loka Yekoiakim okoku loka Yosia, ekabaka loka Yuda, kobala ebe: 
2  “Inera kwanata EJAKAIT, Edeke loka Isirael, neijai ijo, Baruk, ebe: 
3  Ibu kotema atiar, ‘Wu okwe! Abei ai? Naarai eyataki EJAKAIT ican toma arieboka; kapas eidinyaka, kwabo mam adumunit aiyeŋun kere.’ 
4  

Itemari Ŋes kwanata atiar, Inera kwanata EJAKAIT ebe: Koany, aketari ŋin yenabu kaduk, arutori da ŋin yenabu kera; ido eswamakini kwaŋin akwap kere. 
5  

Imoot ijo nuepolok? Sirimoot; naarai ebala EJAKAIT ebe: Koany, ayauni aronis mama ejaas ŋul kere luejai akuan, konye ainakini akoniijar araut aŋatuna kaiboisio kere nuilosenenei.”

